column5: I STOPPED BY AFTER WORK AT 3:45 PM TODAY. THERE IS A CRIMINAL INVESTIGATION GOING ON. LOTS OF HOLES ARE BEING CHAIN SAWED. THEY LOOKED TO BE 3 FT TRIANGLES.THEY SEEM TO BE PUTTING THE CUT PIECES ON THEIR EDGE SO YOU CAN SEE WHERE THEY HAVE CUT. USE EXTREME CAUTION IF YOU PLAN ON HEADING OUT THERE IN THE NEXT COUPLE OF DAYS. ICE LOOKS TO BE ABOUT 3 INCHES THICK FROM WHAT I COULD SEE FROM SHORE.
Hopefully their not looking for a body B.... To many reports of people going through...  G
It seems to be an on going investigation G  OPP AND BARRIE POLICE
Word from a local I spoke to down there at noon today said yes, they are. An apparent suicide is the rumor, one last walk...
Thanks for the heads up Brian!
So ya mean there's a pointy end sticking up?  Sure hope not, couple more days and some sledders will have a rude obstacle if they don't see that.

Yes Erich  They are back there again this morning. The OPP divers are working with the Barrie police. The one I talked to said all he could say was that. As I was leaving, CTV was pulling in. I,ll stop back after work.
Still there are of 4 pm this afternoon. No entry into the lot.  Pretty hush hush.
